==Hunsrik==
===Etymology===
From {{inh|hrx|gmh|slūch|t=slough, skin shed by a snake}}. Cognate with {{cog|de|Schlauch}} and {{cog|en|slough}}.
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|hrx|/ʃlɔjx/}}
===Noun===
{{head|hrx|noun}}
# [[hose]] (flexible tube for water)
